function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	--Edgar tells us to meet him in caldeum and walks away
	local cloneDeserter = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(actorDeserterOverlook_Q4)
	local idPlayer = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(cloneDeserter) then
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(cloneDeserter)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(convStartBark, idPlayer, cloneDeserter)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(cloneDeserter, markerDeserterFadeWalk, "NPC_Walk", false)
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(cloneDeserter, 2.0)
	end
	
end
